    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Variable dark purplish color resembling the color of the fruit of the eggplant, a widely cultivated perennial herb of the nightshade family.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
